title: Grateful Dead Live at San Francisco Civic Auditorium on 1987-01-29
description:
Set 1

Finiculi Finicula, Hell In A Bucket > Sugaree, El Paso, Loser, Little Red Rooster, Brown Eyed Women, Cassidy > Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias > Fire On The Mountain, Looks Like Rain, Terrapin Station > Drums > I Need A Miracle > Stella Blue > Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad > Johnny B. Goode

E: It's All Over Now Baby Blue

Chinese New Year
Chinese Symphony Orchestra Opened

reviews.review_text: Pretty good AUD This show gets off to a bumpy start, threatening to be a repeat of last night's disappointment. Instead, they get it together by the middle of the first and deliver a ragingly good show.
